\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Berry2007"

\end_inset

.
 Some examples of this are further discussed below.
 The objective function is implemented using a series of update functions.
 The update functions are iteratively processed until the approximation
 of 
\begin_inset Formula $VW$
\end_inset

